history.proof: intros l i H. induction l as [|e l' IHl]. - simpl. auto. - simpl. sauto lq: on depth: 3.

exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 2 branches.

original: intros l i H. induction l as [|e l' IHl]. - simpl. auto. - simpl. destruct H as [H1 H2]. apply NoDup_cons_iff in H1. destruct H1 as [H1 H3]. apply IHl in H3. apply NoDup_cons. split. + intro H4. apply H1. apply removeAfterIndex_in in H4. apply H4. + apply H3.
